PublicDescription: A directory write to the woke Level-1 Instruction Cache directory where the woke returned cache line was sourced from the woke Level-2 (L1.5) cache.
A directory write to the woke Level-1 Data Cache directory where the woke installed cache line was sourced from the woke Level-2 (L1.5) cache.

A directory write to the woke Level-1 Instruction Cache directory where the woke installed cache line was sourced from the woke Level-3 cache that is on the woke same book as the woke Instruction cache (Local L2 cache).

A directory write to the woke Level-1 Data Cache directory where the woke installed cache line was source from the woke Level-3 cache that is on the woke same book as the woke Data cache (Local L2 cache).

A directory write to the woke Level-1 Instruction Cache directory where the woke installed cache line was sourced from a Level-3 cache that is not on the woke same book as the woke Instruction cache (Remote L2 cache).

A directory write to the woke Level-1 Data Cache directory where the woke installed cache line was sourced from a Level-3 cache that is not on the woke same book as the woke Data cache (Remote L2 cache).
A directory write to the woke Level-1 Data Cache directory where the woke installed cache line was sourced from memory that is attached to the woke same book as the woke Data cache (Local Memory).

A directory write to the woke Level-1 Instruction Cache where the woke installed cache line was sourced from memory that is attached to the woke s ame book as the woke Instruction cache (Local Memory).

A directory write to the woke Level-1 Data Cache where the woke line was originally in a Read-Only state in the woke cache but has been updated to be in the woke Exclusive state that allows stores to the woke cache line.
A cache line in the woke Level-1 Instruction Cache has been invalidated by a store on the woke same CPU as the woke Level-1 Instruction Cache.
A translation entry has been written into the woke Level-1 Instruction Translation Lookaside Buffer (ITLB1).
A translation entry has been written to the woke Level-1 Data Translation Lookaside Buffer (DTLB1).
A translation entry has been written to the woke Level-2 TLB Page Table Entry arrays.
A translation entry has been written to the woke Level-2 TLB Common Region Segment Table Entry arrays.
A translation entry has been written to the woke Level-2 TLB Common Region Segment Table Entry arrays for a one-megabyte large page translation.
Level-1 Instruction TLB miss in progress. Incremented by one for every cycle an ITLB1 miss is in progress.
Level-1 Data TLB miss in progress. Incremented by one for every cycle an DTLB1 miss is in progress.
Incremented by one for every store sent to Level-2 (L1.5) cache.
